POE-Component-Client-Stomp version 0.01
=======================================

This module is a wrapper around POE::Component::Client::TCP. It provides
support for programs that want to communicate with a Stomp server such as
POE::Component::Server::MessageQueue or ActiveMQ from the Apache Foundation.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  POE::Filter::Stomp
  POE::Component::Client::TCP

